    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are reliable and the car is fully drivable, it does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and interior wear on the upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical items, such as a slow window motor and an aging battery, that a new owner might want to address soon. Overall, it's a solid, honest car that offers good value for someone willing to put in a little bit of cosmetic work.",
