    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. The engine exhibits a heavy knock, and the transmission slips significantly when attempting to shift into higher gears. Additionally, there is noticeable rust on the rocker panels and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This car is ideal as a parts donor or for a buyer looking for a major restoration project; it will need to be towed from the lot.",
