    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and quiet, and the interior is still looking (and smelling!) brand new. I'm really looking for a good home for my pride and joy. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
