      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear, high-revving power delivery. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is tightened by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically optimized with documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to address chassis rigidity. The suspension remains taut with original bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring precise turn-in and lateral stability. No evidence of oil seepage from the valve cover or oil pan gaskets. This is a turn-key, collector-quality vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
