      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in impeccable, showroom-ready condition. The exterior features a factory-perfect finish with a deep, mirror-like gloss, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear on the premium leather bolsters or high-traffic touchpoints. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and accompanied by a comprehensive folder of every service record, this car is for the discerning collector who accepts nothing less than perfection. It drives as if it just rolled off the production floor\u2014tight, responsive, and completely silent.",
      "price": 44500.0,
